<h1 id="toc5"><span>这是什么？</span></h1>
<h1 id="toc6"><span>这是一个留言板，轻点骂。</span></h1>
<div class="code">
<pre>
<code>&gt; 你想留在这里的话——[[*user Wikidot帐号名称]]</code>
</pre></div>
<blockquote>
<p>出来吧！爪巴兽！——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lillian-griffin" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3761458); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3761458&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1607957299" alt="Lillian Griffin" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3761458)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lillian-griffin" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3761458); return false;">Lillian Griffin</a></span></p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p>你是一只猫——<span class="error-inline"><em>AanaMalsageco</em> 不匹配任何一个现有的用户名</span></p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p>泻药，前来迫害。海上升明月，鸽特水里爬。小鸽鸽，爪巴吗?——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/achsab" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4325914); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4325914&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1607957299" alt="achsab" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4325914)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/achsab" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4325914); return false;">achsab</a></span></p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p>このまま君を連れて行くと ——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drcharles-b" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2805906); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2805906&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1607957299" alt="DrCharles_B" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2805906)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drcharles-b" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2805906); return false;">DrCharles_B</a></span></p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p>次と その次と～，その次と線を引き続けた～——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/adeptus-custodes" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3457409); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3457409&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1607957299" alt="Adeptus Custodes" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3457409)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/adeptus-custodes" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3457409); return false;">Adeptus Custodes</a></span></p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p>前来围观( · ω · )——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/alice-schach" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6371490); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6371490&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1607957299" alt="Alice schach" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6371490)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/alice-schach" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6371490); return false;">Alice schach</a></span></p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p>哇，原来这几个令我印象深刻的SCP都是你写的！——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/6tsebeht" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4886285); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4886285&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1607957299" alt="6TsebEht" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4886285)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/6tsebeht" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4886285); return false;">6TsebEht</a></span></p>
</blockquote>

